{"tid":1914122,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"《食食吓譚仔，我好似突然明白咗啲咩……》","createTime":"2020-03-07T10:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T05:43:17.000Z","uid":73724,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"48205107ae1b6a2061da148c92a15a05b9fbef3c","tid":1914122,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:02:35.000Z","msg":"今日我同我女朋友去食譚仔。<br />\n<br />\n好似平時一樣，我嗌咗個過橋。點知食到最後食唔哂，剩底咗粒墨演，但又唔想畀人知我食剩咗咁柒。<br />\n<br />\n女朋友話搵啲湯埋咗佢咪得咯。我照做，點知佢又浮起咗。<br />\n<br />\n佢又話搵支湯羹㩒住佢咪得咯。我又照做。<br />\n<br />\n只見個湯搖呀搖，水波一下又一下咁衝擊住個湯羹。最後都敵不過浪潮，沉沒於紅湯之中。而墨演最後亦徐徐浮起。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢一刻，我好似突然明白咗啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。"},{"pid":"f4b0e8b5299f1c455e6a31de049c65ea4f2d4a9a","tid":1914122,"uid":211362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfcb8c145f8676089593e7c681aafc5906994308","tid":1914122,"uid":116143,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"我突然明白樓主係on9, block"},{"pid":"fc3bc0f172bed4d17e5b62f0c15d3ff2dcb8a166","tid":1914122,"uid":199893,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"真相同墨演一樣<br />\n最後點都會浮面<br />\n黑警，屌你老母呀"},{"pid":"bbbab5b0da22846a6614d64390773a09e7065cae","tid":1914122,"uid":73724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc3bc0f172bed4d17e5b62f0c15d3ff2dcb8a166","tid":1914122,"uid":199893,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"真相同墨演一樣<br />\n最後點都會浮面<br />\n黑警，屌你老母呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9f52037e2f4f1a1fad1fd14d0fd77ecbdeaa10","tid":1914122,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re